Find Substring in a String | Check if a given substring exists in a string. |

import java.util.*;
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String str = "Hello World";
        String s = "World";
        System.out.println("Substring of a string: "+ isSubString(str,s));
    }
    public static boolean isSubString(String str,String s){
        return str.contains(s);
    }
}

output:
Substring of a string: true
